<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>We received your Sendvery beta access request</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f5; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table role="presentation" width="560" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #0f766e; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800;">Sendvery</h1>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px;">
                            <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 20px; color: #18181b;">Thanks, {{ name }} — we got your request</h2>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52525b;">
                                You asked about the <strong>{{ plan.value|capitalize }}</strong> plan. Sendvery hosted is in private beta — I'm onboarding small batches at a time.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52525b;">
                                I'll personally reply within a few working days with next steps. If you have something specific in mind, just hit reply.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #52525b;">
                                In the meantime, you can <a href="https://sendvery.com/open-source" style="color: #0f766e;">run Sendvery on your own server</a> — it's open source under AGPL-3.0 and self-hosting is always free.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 32px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #71717a;">— Jan, Sendvery</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
